# ALT Kiosk — Architecture Refactor Plan

## 📋 Executive Summary

Refactor the kiosk system so the **Python backend becomes the single source of truth** for all business logic, employee data, and cloud communication. The React frontend will communicate **only** with the local Python backend — never directly with the cloud.

