- [ ] React sends only `{ command: "IDENTIFY", params: { employee_id } }`
- [ ] Python looks up employee from local SQLite (not cloud)
- [ ] Python triggers fingerprint scan and compares locally
- [ ] Python sends `identify_result` → `fingerprint_state` → `verify_result` events
- [ ] Scan logs are saved locally and queued for cloud upload
- [ ] Works fully offline (after initial sync)

#### Estimated Effort: **8-10 hours**

